__data__.text: Eric (also known as 何俊/何比) is skilled in AI and works at Amazon. He is also a popular friend, known for his filial piety and decent basketball skills (though not as good as zzn).  Abie (憋哥) is Eric's teammate in a CS gaming group (including Final, 段神, 凯神, 小瘦哥/Jason, 刘坤, and 马棚) and is considered skilled despite being introverted. Abie has a 4-year-old son named 兜兜.  小瘦哥 (Jason) excels at sniping in shooting games. Final is an all-around skilled CS player. 段神 is adept at using in-game items. 吴非 works in AI at Amazon. 马棚 is a skilled and experienced driver.  Abie's income is modest. 小瘦哥 enjoys trips to Korea.  Abie is currently learning about AI applications and is under pressure. "O孝子" refers to being devoted to OpenAI.  911 is considered superior to 718.  七七, 妮妮, and 珂珂 are also mentioned as being cute.
